HIV pixel clustering, xdim=5, ydim=4, 1 pass, 5 replicates

Candace Liu

April 8, 2021

  • Gaussian blur sigma=2, k=20 (pixel metaclusters)
  • z-score cap=3 for consensus hierarchical clustering
  • For each pixel, divide each marker by total (each pixel sums to 1)
